eplyTime":"2016-12-19T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我好想快d遇到另一個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好習慣佢每晚打黎 <br />\n我有咩都會同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢會同我一齊解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ee833f0f6f587fc64a551bebba03ba519b1330","tid":46552,"uid":57870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寄情工作中，但有少少空出嚟嘅時間都會沉返落去，有時仲會忍唔住text佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82053cd7bafc17b736c1503c4bfb07009b50b4b","tid":46552,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>習慣咗啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係習慣左 好似冇人填補到呢個角色咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以令自己忙啲會有用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵個地方平靜地好好咁整理下思緒啦巴打 愛情路上有邊個冇受傷過 好好咁收拾對ex既感情 想喊就喊想發癲就發癲 咁樣會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係你既始終都係你既 當係上左一堂 送走一個重要既過客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67232fef991290206d21a1a88a599fbe0ce831be","tid":46552,"uid":57870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我好想快d遇到另一個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算𠵱家遇到，都投放唔到感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e761fa18b3c5f746b81b727b9106c1437d447f","tid":46552,"uid":12595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"自己獨處下，人再大d 都一定要學識自己獨處"},{"pid":"fb4bc545287131526c0b587ec34f2f70dda02078","tid":46552,"uid":54110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>習慣咗啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係習慣左 好似冇人填補到呢個角色咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以令自己忙啲會有用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵個地方平靜地好好咁整理下思緒啦巴打 愛情路上有邊個冇受傷過 好好咁收拾對ex既感情 想喊就喊想發癲就發癲 咁樣會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係你既始終都係你既 當係上左一堂 送走一個重要既過客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係 的確要去收拾呢段感情 唔好再拖泥帶水"},{"pid":"19258c068310ed5327d79660b3c1c96834f149ac","tid":46552,"uid":54110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己獨處下，人再大d 都一定要學識自己獨處</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前就係自己呃自己已經冇問過可以一個人<br />\n可能要多啲時間"}]}